en_US: Ability to run Trade Assignment and Margin Calculation processes. This process does not affect transaction details.
Ability to facilitate margin calls and administer respective movements
Ability to facilitate margin calls, administer respective movements, and approve movements
Ability to add/edit reference data required for margin call maintenance. This process does not affect transaction details.
Ability to create and edit agreements. This process does not affect transaction details but rather static data input only.
Ability to create, edit and approve changes to agreements. This process does not affect transaction details but rather static data input only.
Ability to read agreements, trade exposure, margin calls and movements
Ability to approve movements and agreement changes
Ability to facilitate and settle movements to satisfy margin calls and interest payouts
Ability to administer delivery/payment instructions. Does not have the ability to approve movements.
Ability to execute any operation minus capability to edit movements, agreements, and approve. Currently not in use.
